      </article>
      <article class="svc-card">
        <div class="svc-bg">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522337360788-8b13dee7a37e?w=600&q=75" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="svc-icon"><svg width="19" height="19" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Coloración &amp; Mechas</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Balayage, highlights, babylights, color global y decoloración. Colores que duran y respetan tu cabello.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="svc-card">
        <div class="svc-bg">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487412947147-5cebf100ffc2?w=600&q=75" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="svc-icon"><svg width="19" height="19" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg></div>
